Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.80,0:00:04.15,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,布里塔尼亚少年  鲁路修
Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.27,0:00:06.07,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拥有两个力量
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.47,0:00:07.60,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一个是Geass
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.03,0:00:11.87,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对任何对手都能下令使其绝对服从的力量
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.66,0:00:14.37,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一个是黑色骑士团
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.68,0:00:19.39,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为破坏父亲统治的布里塔尼亚的他自己的军队
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.51,0:00:23.95,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鲁路修借ZERO这个代号行动起来了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.30,0:00:26.05,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为了替母亲报仇
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.50,0:00:30.94,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还有为了创造妹妹娜娜莉能幸福生活的世界
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.51,0:00:34.96,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这行动会导致怎样的结果
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.50,0:00:38.23,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在谁也不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.12,0:02:12.99,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fad(600,0)\pos(424,395)}STAGE 9
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.02,0:02:12.99,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fad(600,0)\pos(424,430)}Refrain
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.13,0:02:17.83,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,河口的会议中心宾馆终于开始重建工程了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.09,0:02:21.04,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,ZERO宣布黑色骑士团以来已经两周以上了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.33,0:02:23.69,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,结果还是没有找到确实的证据吗
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.93,0:02:26.17,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,逃走路线被隐蔽起来了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.53,0:02:29.39,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,解放人质还有引导车辆到海岸
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.90,0:02:41.98,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,卡莲
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.53,0:02:43.26,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.46,0:02:45.60,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起  吵醒你了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.79,0:02:46.68,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又来了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.86,0:02:49.86,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起  这次是梯子倒下来了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.09,0:02:51.34,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快收拾干净
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.60,0:02:53.49,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很快就是去学校的时间了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.80,0:02:56.78,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小姐  最近您经常去学校呢
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.06,0:02:58.08,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是不是交上了朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.25,0:02:59.95,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这和你没有关系吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.08,0:03:06.21,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快消失吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.12,0:03:16.13,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽说是福利
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.35,0:03:18.70,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是把这东西给11区人实在是太可惜了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.97,0:03:21.15,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以才流到你们那儿啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.38,0:03:24.33,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没什么  11区人减少一点才好呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.95,0:03:29.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,报酬就汇到你太太的户头上
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.93,0:03:32.94,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,科奈莉娅殿下是武人
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.16,0:03:35.61,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对这种东西不会熟悉的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.40,0:03:41.10,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,灯  快打开灯
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.30,0:03:46.60,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  你是
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.50,0:03:49.89,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,黑色骑士团
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.93,0:03:59.81,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真少见  卡莲居然会打瞌睡
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.03,0:04:01.31,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  稍微有点…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.76,0:04:03.63,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你干脆做鲁路修的徒弟算了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.88,0:04:05.76,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那家伙是打瞌睡的强者
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.15,0:04:08.80,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是在打瞌睡么
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.10,0:04:11.34,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都不知道他每天晚上在做什么
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.60,0:04:13.99,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那家伙上课有一半时间都在睡觉
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.77,0:04:19.85,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在埃洛拉主战线EU发动了攻势
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.97,0:04:19.85,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs20\fsp-1}{\fad(100,100)\a6)}[Ellora：印度孟买东北部小村庄，今名贝鲁莱]
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.24,0:04:21.23,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,从我们的角度说
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.46,0:04:24.86,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也不能一直被这个11区给绊住手脚
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.42,0:04:28.35,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要把内政处理干净  让那边升格为安全地区
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.06,0:04:31.74,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽说为了这些  击溃恐怖组织也是重要的任务
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.96,0:04:34.44,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但在11区中蔓延的药物
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.66,0:04:36.67,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Refrain的问题也很严峻
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.11,0:04:39.20,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为这个  生产力也下降了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.74,0:04:42.85,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一定要把中华联邦的主输送线给截断
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.17,0:04:43.98,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你明白了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.18,0:04:45.97,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的  请务必小心
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.18,0:04:48.60,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你也是  别再从租界出去了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.86,0:04:51.55,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,姐姐  关于黑色骑士团的事
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.80,0:04:53.85,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让他们再逍遥法外一段时间吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.05,0:04:56.15,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也欠他们救你这个情
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.80,0:04:58.46,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是等我回来后
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.29,0:05:05.67,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我会把这个区弄干净了再交给你
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.93,0:05:08.02,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以不要想危险的事
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.36,0:05:09.87,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好吗  由菲
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.32,0:05:13.62,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为是那个男人
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.82,0:05:16.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是布里塔尼亚皇帝的孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.84,0:05:17.78,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,话说回来
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.14,0:05:20.35,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你也是呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.69,0:05:23.80,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是  现在还…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.88,0:05:27.60,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个时候ZERO说的话的意思
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.92,0:05:30.29,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是不是指还会继续呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.90,0:05:31.98,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,朱雀
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.18,0:05:33.60,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果是你的话会怎么想呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.81,0:05:35.37,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对于ZERO的行为
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.74,0:05:37.85,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还有  我会…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.72,0:05:45.75,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是辛苦啊  二重生活
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.95,0:05:47.49,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快点  朱雀  那边那边
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.70,0:05:49.32,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,笨蛋  住手啊朱雀
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.94,0:05:51.29,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,住手  快住手
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.65,0:05:52.84,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起  鲁路修
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.12,0:05:54.04,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为是会长命令
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.40,0:05:55.80,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的脸明明在笑啊  喂
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.00,0:05:57.20,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要动
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.30,0:05:59.70,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早上好喵~
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.85,0:06:02.04,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早…上好
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.75,0:06:04.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是什么
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.33,0:06:05.86,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊啦  没有和你说过吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.06,0:06:07.84,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿瑟的欢迎会
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.75,0:06:09.59,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真和平啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.50,0:06:12.77,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,危机期间就好好享受嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.98,0:06:14.56,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们也准备了卡莲的份
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.90,0:06:15.50,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.83,0:06:17.83,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,作为上次我对你说了奇怪的话的道歉
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.03,0:06:18.70,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你要哪件?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.90,0:06:20.10,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎  我也要?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.67,0:06:21.93,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,卡莲就不需要了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.76,0:06:24.63,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早就带着(假面)了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.90,0:06:27.65,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你怎么不上电视
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.87,0:06:29.31,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一定会很受欢迎的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.62,0:06:31.50,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你怎么看  电视明星小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.70,0:06:33.08,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  话题转移到那边啦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.35,0:06:35.30,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要开这种玩笑了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.59,0:06:37.47,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那之后我们可辛苦了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.70,0:06:39.64,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,每时每刻都被人围着
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.84,0:06:40.67,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,逼着追问问题
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.90,0:06:46.13,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这一个礼拜连学校都出不了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.50,0:06:49.99,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算这样  为什么连我们也要禁止外出啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.19,0:06:51.77,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这就叫友情吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.07,0:06:57.69,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们不求同日而生 只求同日而死  By~三国志
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.07,0:06:59.02,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs20\fsp-1}{\fad(100,100)\a6)}[引自三国志中桃园结义时的话 原文为不求同年同月同日生 只愿同年同月同日死]
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.89,0:06:59.12,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这难道是在求婚
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.32,0:07:01.24,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要死也要拖人下水
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.44,0:07:02.40,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你真过分
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.65,0:07:03.70,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吧  朱雀
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.52,0:07:05.60,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.49,0:07:08.71,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家又能在一起
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.99,0:07:10.06,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.17,0:07:12.60,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.88,0:07:14.45,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这时候应该笑嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.53,0:07:19.71,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但这就是朱雀的优点呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.97,0:07:23.08,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,希望他偶尔也能考虑一下周围的气氛呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.30,0:07:24.40,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.60,0:07:26.42,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你啊  那只不过是开玩笑的啦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.50,0:07:30.72,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊  我救了大家
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.18,0:07:34.87,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,宾馆劫持事件华丽登场之后
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.10,0:07:37.82,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,世界的目光集中在黑色骑士团身上了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.30,0:07:42.19,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,黑色骑士团正如ZERO的宣言般是弱者的朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.50,0:07:44.42,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不把平民卷进来的恐怖行动
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.62,0:07:45.73,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蛮横的军队
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.93,0:07:47.40,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还有贪污的政治家
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.60,0:07:48.66,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,盈利主义至上的企业
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.86,0:07:51.30,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,犯罪组织之类的法律无法惩治的邪恶
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.50,0:07:53.14,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,单方面进行制裁
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.19,0:07:57.43,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们瞬间就成了英雄
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.12,0:07:59.35,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,协助者也增加了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.66,0:08:02.10,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也再次得到了KnightMare
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.62,0:08:05.24,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但并不都只是好事
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.60,0:08:06.55,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.79,0:08:08.66,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要玩这个了  黑色骑士团这种
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.89,0:08:09.67,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.92,0:08:12.38,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不能说布里塔尼亚的坏话
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.62,0:08:14.45,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们可是11区住民啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.11,0:08:18.70,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,首领的ZERO杀了克洛维斯
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.07,0:08:21.98,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,同伴间想要知道他真实面目的人也很多
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.22,0:08:23.76,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也是一样
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.06,0:08:27.96,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是总觉得如果强逼他的话他就会消失
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.30,0:08:31.50,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,或许现在已到了他不在就不行的地步了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.70,0:08:32.80,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对我们来说
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.00,0:08:34.45,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我说最近啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.39,0:08:37.14,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很少陪我们了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.60,0:08:38.41,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.90,0:08:40.30,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.23,0:08:46.80,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你没事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.81,0:08:54.67,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么民众会帮助救了由菲米娅的家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.89,0:08:59.05,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,京都也说要把红莲二式交给黑色骑士团
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.26,0:09:00.58,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,给那种半吊子?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.79,0:09:02.18,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他们根本不是反抗组织
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.51,0:09:04.50,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,证据就是他们杀了草壁中校
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.71,0:09:06.60,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,中校是自杀的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.80,0:09:08.80,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也有传闻说他们没有阻止
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.07,0:09:09.97,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,藤堂中校
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.17,0:09:12.19,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,无论怎么说  照这样下去的话
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.14,0:09:20.55,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,卡莲小姐  卡莲小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.25,0:09:23.30,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,会长
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.50,0:09:25.60,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有点东西想给你
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.50,0:09:29.51,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,该带她去哪里呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.71,0:09:31.20,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,客室  还是
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.40,0:09:32.41,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去我的房间
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.61,0:09:33.90,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,遵命
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.38,0:09:38.40,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊啦  说是你朋友  我还以为是男性呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.60,0:09:40.23,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大清早回来不去上学
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.49,0:09:42.30,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像还会进出贫民区呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.60,0:09:45.27,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,趁着你父亲在本国就任意妄为
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.47,0:09:47.99,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,血缘真是无可争辩的事实
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.87,0:09:53.12,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,享受父亲不在时的逍遥是你才对吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.14,0:09:59.14,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,该怎么办  该怎么办
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.45,0:10:01.44,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你到底在干什么
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.64,0:10:04.05,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起  太太  对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.30,0:10:05.70,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是没用
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.11,0:10:08.33,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只有靠女人身体这一个本钱
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.41,0:10:11.67,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是个复杂的家庭呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.74,0:10:14.45,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想要交给我的是什么
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.65,0:10:16.41,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爷爷拜托我的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.69,0:10:17.70,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,学园长?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.50,0:10:20.50,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,中学以来的成绩证明书
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.67,0:10:24.62,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在学校不方便给你
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.06,0:10:26.97,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已经知道了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.29,0:10:31.36,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是布里塔尼亚人和11区人混血这件事
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.31,0:10:35.37,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,刚才那个是我的继母
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.70,0:10:39.44,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真正的母亲是打翻花瓶的那个迟钝女佣
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.29,0:10:44.89,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,父亲是修坦菲尔德的当家吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.28,0:10:46.92,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,母亲是一个笨蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.18,0:10:49.35,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最后成了佣人被使唤
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.75,0:10:51.24,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又没能力做什么工作
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.46,0:10:55.17,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算再怎么被看不起也只能傻乎乎地笑
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.71,0:10:58.04,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明明不用特地住在这个家里的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.32,0:11:00.40,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其实就是厚着脸皮的要住在这里
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.64,0:11:02.04,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对着以前的男人
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.46,0:11:04.18,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你讨厌你母亲吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.39,0:11:05.94,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是觉得麻烦而已
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.26,0:11:07.91,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是沉重的话题呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.15,0:11:11.92,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正妻  外遇和女儿居然一起住这种事
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.30,0:11:13.48,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也不完全是这样哦
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.82,0:11:15.55,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,衣食住行也没有不方便
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.85,0:11:19.22,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,并不是…不能忍的事
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.50,0:11:20.43,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.19,0:11:22.03,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.34,0:11:24.60,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算每一个小事都能够忍耐
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.88,0:11:26.33,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果全都累积起来
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.57,0:11:28.33,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总有一天会崩溃的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.77,0:11:30.82,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不用担心
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.04,0:11:33.18,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然我很想要知道别人的秘密
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.43,0:11:35.18,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是没有说出去的兴趣
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.25,0:11:54.62,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别在那种情况下哭啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.92,0:11:56.04,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是个让人害羞的家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.34,0:11:58.10,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请称这为直率
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.80,0:12:01.45,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过大家都得救了真是太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.70,0:12:03.80,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,多亏了黑色骑士团那些人
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.22,0:12:07.88,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要逮捕犯罪者的话
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.24,0:12:09.64,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让警察来不就好了嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.20,0:12:11.95,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他们为什么不这么做
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.08,0:12:15.40,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一定是认为警察没法做到吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.07,0:12:16.98,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,警察这种
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.33,0:12:18.14,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算现在不行
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.60,0:12:21.10,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么去做警察  从内部改变不就行了嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.50,0:12:22.46,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,本来想要改变
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.80,0:12:25.38,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最后却被各种各样的规则束缚住
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.78,0:12:29.57,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那只有等做了最大程度的努力去改变才能说这种话
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.04,0:12:30.91,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不做这种事
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.33,0:12:33.11,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他们所作的只能说是独善
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.45,0:12:34.56,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,独善?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.89,0:12:36.49,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他们所说的恶到底是什么
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.84,0:12:39.39,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以什么作为基准都不知道不是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.74,0:12:42.10,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,单方面的自我满足而已
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.85,0:12:46.28,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只有你们两个人?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.18,0:12:50.70,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那我走了  我一定要回军队去了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.45,0:12:52.41,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,回见  莎莉
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.47,0:12:54.78,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,回见
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.98,0:13:07.21,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个  鲁路修
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.14,0:13:09.96,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下次
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.60,0:13:12.08,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果有空的话
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.47,0:13:12.94,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和我
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.38,0:13:13.84,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.14,0:13:15.86,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说一定要回军队去了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.15,0:13:18.21,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,回去
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.80,0:13:20.74,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那里是你的归处吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.39,0:13:22.24,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Refrain?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.54,0:13:23.56,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,毒品
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.91,0:13:26.18,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,特征是让人觉得回到了过去
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.48,0:13:27.39,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,应该很好卖
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.69,0:13:28.63,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,特别是对于日本人来说
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.02,0:13:30.11,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谁都会怀念啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.41,0:13:33.41,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被布里塔尼亚占领之前的日本
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.70,0:13:37.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是针对日本人的药物
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.33,0:13:38.70,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不能放着不管
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.34,0:13:42.14,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,无赖的补给物资抵达了之后马上就行动
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.51,0:13:43.50,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,听说补给增加了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.88,0:13:46.46,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想要成为同伴的人也有很多
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.18,0:13:48.94,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,黑色骑士团真是受欢迎啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.25,0:13:50.92,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为是正义的朋友嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.77,0:13:53.60,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,弹药到了我再联系你
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.80,0:13:57.66,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你倒是说点什么啊  你这个11区人
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.91,0:13:59.22,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快道歉啊  道歉
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.54,0:14:01.90,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,11区人不是很擅长低头吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.12,0:14:02.80,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,11区人
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.50,0:14:06.60,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鲁路修
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.03,0:14:07.90,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对手有五个人
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.32,0:14:09.39,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不可能赢的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.69,0:14:11.30,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么就能放着不管吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.66,0:14:12.24,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你好好看看
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.58,0:14:13.91,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被打的那个11区人
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.93,0:14:18.65,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,随便帮助他试试看
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.15,0:14:22.54,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个11区人从明天起就没法做生意了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.96,0:14:25.70,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他是自己选择成为布里塔尼亚的奴隶的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.09,0:14:28.78,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在租界工作就是这个意思
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.11,0:14:29.75,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算这么说
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.06,0:14:31.61,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有意见吗  你们
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.22,0:14:33.61,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,11区人很可怜吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.00,0:14:36.76,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是吧  想成为他们的同伴吧  是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.04,0:14:37.79,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么可能
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.74,0:14:41.68,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们也差不多厌倦了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.15,0:14:43.73,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,欺负11区人这种事
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.80,0:14:48.90,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真无聊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.25,0:14:50.37,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去游戏机厅么
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.77,0:14:51.75,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没有钱啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.99,0:14:54.63,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是容易厌倦的家伙呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.92,0:14:58.77,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.01,0:15:02.71,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,布里塔尼亚的学生
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.56,0:15:04.81,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,欢迎光临
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.17,0:15:07.28,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想要来一份加利福尼亚热狗吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.57,0:15:09.71,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,男朋友吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.14,0:15:11.65,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可以的话  两位请吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.95,0:15:13.76,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还有冰淇淋哦
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.54,0:15:17.40,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,11区与还是日本的时候比起来
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.70,0:15:19.11,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可以说是好多了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.61,0:15:21.69,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,多亏成了布里塔尼亚的殖民地
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.06,0:15:23.10,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,军事也好经济也好
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.44,0:15:24.69,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都大幅的安定下来
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.97,0:15:26.33,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还能拿到市民权
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.67,0:15:28.61,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要到政府去办手续
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.95,0:15:31.01,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不就能成为名誉布里塔尼亚人了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.43,0:15:32.86,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,剩下的就是自尊的问题了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.21,0:15:36.32,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过  也能理解重视这个的心情
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.78,0:15:37.51,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然后呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.32,0:15:39.53,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,知道了这些
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.95,0:15:42.12,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鲁路修·兰佩洛奇是怎么想的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.58,0:15:43.60,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想要干什么
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.96,0:15:44.74,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没什么
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.12,0:15:47.46,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的头脑似乎非常好
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.76,0:15:48.67,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但总是口头上说
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.00,0:15:50.26,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,莎莉总是在惋惜
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.56,0:15:52.01,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鲁鲁不去努力
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.40,0:15:53.89,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,枉费头脑那么好
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.21,0:15:55.93,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以我才什么都不做
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.80,0:15:58.83,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,刚才的11区人也很清楚
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.23,0:16:02.73,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,向布里塔尼亚人低头就能生活得很好
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.07,0:16:09.39,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你觉得你很帅吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.70,0:16:10.64,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱着这种想法
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.94,0:16:12.73,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看不起这个世界吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.49,0:16:17.04,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对你这种想法抱有期待的我真是笨蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.30,0:16:19.61,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还以为你是个正经男人呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.88,0:16:31.99,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个ORANGE事件
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.44,0:16:33.50,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.12,0:16:37.08,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个枢木朱雀强夺事件的时候
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.44,0:16:39.40,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,卿说您没有记忆是真的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.70,0:16:41.60,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我没有指望你会相信我
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.90,0:16:42.43,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.86,0:16:45.04,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其实我也在新宿那次事件中
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.42,0:16:47.26,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,经历过丧失记忆的情况
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.64,0:16:48.14,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.49,0:16:49.97,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,恢复意识的时候
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.27,0:16:52.09,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Sutherland已经被夺走了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.51,0:16:54.20,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且在丧失记忆之前
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.50,0:16:56.97,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我遇见了一个穿学生服的少年
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.35,0:16:58.52,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就是说那个学生?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.88,0:17:00.23,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我记不起脸了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.65,0:17:03.41,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是我认为有调查的价值
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.84,0:17:06.92,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,ZERO那家伙在想什么
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.46,0:17:09.07,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽说要打倒布里塔尼亚
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.48,0:17:11.86,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,做的事不就是在帮警察嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.29,0:17:14.89,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是被人感谢的感觉并不坏啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.19,0:17:16.07,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是就是
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.37,0:17:17.84,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在网络已经是英雄了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.80,0:17:19.82,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.13,0:17:21.68,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样做真的就好了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.98,0:17:22.80,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,卡莲
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.20,0:17:26.78,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,ZERO的信号
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.11,0:17:28.43,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真亏他能进去
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.73,0:17:31.47,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,每一次都是  用的什么方法啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.60,0:17:38.17,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,名古屋的部分搞定了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.50,0:17:40.36,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,租界里很安全的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.77,0:17:46.55,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,黑色骑士团  参上
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.44,0:17:48.49,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是入侵者
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.90,0:17:52.15,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,KnightMare  怎么会
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.45,0:17:53.46,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别开玩笑了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.43,0:17:59.21,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,KnightMare果然很厉害
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.50,0:18:01.32,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要有一架就有压倒性优势
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.90,0:18:10.72,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,日本  日本
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.00,0:18:12.80,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的  下个月就要结婚了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.10,0:18:15.26,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,升职了  这次是去巴黎
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.58,0:18:17.27,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下个礼拜的烟花大会  一起去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.59,0:18:20.49,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,交给我了  日本的技术是世界第一的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.82,0:18:21.99,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Refrain
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.39,0:18:25.27,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已经确定了  去留学的事  我真行
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.16,0:18:27.30,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果全都累积起来
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.61,0:18:29.37,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总有一天会崩溃的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.86,0:18:30.55,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.86,0:18:31.98,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以我
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.28,0:18:33.01,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂  喂
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.33,0:18:34.75,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,跑起来很危险啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.60,0:18:39.88,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妈妈?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.85,0:18:47.37,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我说直人
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.70,0:18:50.24,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不好好看着卡莲怎么行
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.47,0:18:53.96,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你这个女人是多么的弱小
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.28,0:18:55.33,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,依赖布里塔尼亚
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.63,0:18:56.35,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,依赖男人
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.68,0:18:57.70,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这次又是毒品
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.05,0:18:59.46,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哥哥已经不在了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.89,0:19:00.46,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再这样
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.42,0:19:05.83,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Knight Police?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.47,0:19:10.40,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那不是警察的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.72,0:19:11.52,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,串通在一起的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.90,0:19:12.20,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,玉城
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.50,0:19:13.35,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.61,0:19:15.16,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我调查的时候  的确是
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.46,0:19:16.74,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,该死的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.02,0:19:30.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真碍事
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.80,0:19:33.58,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.03,0:19:35.12,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我明明不需要
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.81,0:19:37.92,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明明不需要
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.80,0:19:47.78,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,卡莲  直人
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.82,0:19:58.52,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和KnightMare做对手的话
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.74,0:20:05.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快…逃
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.56,0:20:07.99,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快逃  你这个笨蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.90,0:20:09.85,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我在这里
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.80,0:20:12.50,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我一直在你身边
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.90,0:20:13.54,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,卡莲
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.91,0:20:15.21,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我在你身边
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.81,0:20:19.62,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.98,0:20:21.92,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以才一直待在那个家中的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.32,0:20:23.91,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只为了这种事
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.47,0:20:25.33,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你真蠢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.60,0:20:35.58,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,笨蛋是
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.92,0:20:36.99,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我才对
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.86,0:20:51.65,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,卡莲
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.35,0:21:00.01,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太好了  卡莲
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.37,0:21:02.75,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你能成为布里塔尼亚人了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.10,0:21:04.10,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样的话
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.40,0:21:06.03,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就不会被打了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.35,0:21:09.72,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也能自由地打电话  去旅行
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.10,0:21:12.85,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是母亲…吗
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.14,0:21:17.34,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虚伪的眼泪会伤害人
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.08,0:21:20.36,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虚伪的笑容会伤害自己
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.78,0:21:26.20,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,毒品的后遗症
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.56,0:21:28.37,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,基本无法进行对话
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.71,0:21:31.41,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,需要时间才能康复
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.17,0:21:35.15,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,判决下来了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.55,0:21:36.82,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,二十年
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.69,0:21:40.58,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你等着
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.91,0:21:43.89,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妈妈出来之前我一定会改变给您看
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.50,0:21:47.83,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我和妈妈能够正常生活的世界
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.18,0:21:50.24,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以  所以
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.15,0:21:55.68,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,加油
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.02,0:21:58.57,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,加油  卡莲
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.34,0:22:00.59,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的女儿
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.28,0:22:08.51,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我会加油
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.77,0:22:15.86,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我会加油的
Dialogue: 0,0:23:48.49,0:23:50.02,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,过去的回忆?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:50.12,0:23:52.52,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能怀念那种东西的人是幸福的
Dialogue: 0,0:23:52.80,0:23:55.44,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为他们相信明天一定会到来
Dialogue: 0,0:23:55.61,0:23:56.45,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是
Dialogue: 0,0:23:56.51,0:23:58.71,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谁能保证那种事一定会实现
Dialogue: 0,0:23:59.10,0:24:01.39,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果卡莲想要跨越它的话
Dialogue: 0,0:24:01.62,0:24:02.74,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,相信她也行
Dialogue: 0,0:24:02.91,0:24:03.87,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对
Dialogue: 0,0:24:04.03,0:24:06.64,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们只能活在现在
